Show Moonlight current state:ph_check_app_name -s -a Moonlight | more
Show Moonlight run account:ph_get_app_user Moonlight
Start or switch to Moonlight:startmoon.sh | more
Stop Moonlight:stopmoon.sh force | more
Restart Moonlight:restartmoon.sh | more
Install Moonlight and integrate with PieHelper:confapps_ph.sh -p inst -a Moonlight
Remove Moonlight from PieHelper and uninstall:confapps_ph.sh -p rem -a Moonlight
Update Moonlight to the latest version (only if installed as a package):ph_update_pkg $PH_MOON_PKG_NAME
Configure Moonlight:confapps_ph.sh -p conf -a Moonlight
List/Select shared game(s) for Moonlight streaming:listmoon_ph.sh
Go to the OptsManagement for Moonlight submenu:ph_show_menu OptsManagement_Moonlight
Go to the TTYManagement for Moonlight submenu:ph_show_menu TTYManagement_Moonlight
Go to Main menu:ph_show_menu Main
Go to Apps menu:ph_show_menu Apps
Open Shell to home directory (Type 'CTRL-D' to return):cd;/bin/bash
Return to previous screen:return
